commit message: Add support for integer types in settings mapped to database
Allow TCP connections to more than one destination to be initiated in parallel, use thread-safe synchronized locking mechanism
Handle SIP addresses (re-)dialed from the call log
Allow call to proceed when ZRTP has failed
Move ShoddyTrustManager from TcpSocket to opentelecoms.org-util
Move AppendingTrustManager from TcpSocket to opentelecoms.org-util
Only init the SSLContext once and share it between threads
